Team Listing Screen:

Fetch teams created/joined by the current user.

Create/Edit Team Screen:

Upload logo to Firebase Storage.

Add team to Firestore with members.

Member Management:

Display colored badges for statuses.

Option to re-invite/remove members.

Captain Assignment:

Default: creator is captain.

Can change only to Accepted member.

Start Registration Button:

Enabled only if all 5 members accepted.
